1
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:26,920
Lu Jingheng,

2
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,160
are you done or not?

3
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,560
Before this matter is made clear,

4
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,420
we are not done.

5
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,280
I told you.

6
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:33,960
It's in the past.

7
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,200
It's no big deal.

8
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,640
You took a risk going to that hospital to investigate.

9
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,320
If I hadn't worried about you and followed you,

10
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,850
you would have been caught.

11
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,440
What exactly are you investigating?

12
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,320
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

13
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,560
I won't cause you trouble,

14
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,200
let alone the Lu family.

15
00:01:48,759 --> 00:01:49,479
Between you and me,

16
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,440
do we have to draw such a clear line?

17
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,200
Yes.

18
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,080
We are just a couple on the surface.

19
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,920
We will go our separate ways one day.

20
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,920
Can't we just mind our own business?

21
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,720
In your eyes,

22
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,410
are we just a couple on the surface?

23
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,920
Hello, Shuyi.

24
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,610
I'll be right there.

25
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,000
Miss Wen.

26
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,800
What's the matter again?

27
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,640
She doesn't sound very well.

28
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,600
Then you can go.

29
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,780
I'll be right back.

30
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,800
Mr. Lu, please.

31
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,120
Jingheng, you're here.

32
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,320
Shuyi, why are you so drunk?

33
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,400
I knew that in this world,

34
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:15,560
you're the only one who cares about me.

35
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,820
Stop drinking.

36
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,480
Just get drunk with me today,

37
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,520
okay?

38
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,040
Shuyi, get some good rest.

39
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,320
Jingheng.

40
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,680
If time stopped at this second,

41
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:58,280
would you be able to stay by my side forever?

42
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,520
I have to go home.

43
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,570
Zhixia is still waiting for me.

44
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,320
What if I was the one who stayed?

45
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:11,520
I'd be the one waiting for you at home,

46
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,880
right?

47
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,680
Shuyi, you're drunk.

48
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,730
I'm not drunk, Lu Jingheng.

49
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,279
Shen Zhixia already has all of you.

50
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,860
Just let me have you for one night.

51
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,040
Can't you?

52
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:27,960
Shuyi.

53
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,570
Your drunken words,

54
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:31,520
I will forget them once I walk out this door.

55
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,400
I hope when you sober up tomorrow morning,

56
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,730
you can forget them too.

57
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,680
You've been drinking. You can't drive.

58
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,080
I can get a driver.

59
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,480
What if I insist you stay tonight?

60
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:56,400
Lu Jingheng, I want to marry you.

61
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,460
Let's get married.

62
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,240
Please help me.

63
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,640
Just pretend.

64
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,960
If you propose,

65
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,760
my family will definitely agree.

66
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:06,220
My dad is forcing me to marry someone abroad,

67
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,760
but I don't want to marry a stranger.

68
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,920
Shuyi, calm down.

69
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,720
You want me to propose to you,

70
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,360
I can't do it.

71
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,440
I'm sorry about

72
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,480
what happened back then.

73
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:48,360
But even if I were given another chance,

74
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,450
I would still make the same choice.

75
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,680
Shen Zhixia,

76
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,840
you must be very proud of yourself right now.

77
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,900
It doesn't matter.

78
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:18,040
I'll wait and see who suffers more,

79
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:21,820
the one who can't get it or the one who gets it and loses it again.

80
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,840
Just go live with her!

81
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,560
I'm hungry.

82
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,520
I'm going to take a shower first.

83
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:48,409
Aren't you going back to your own room?

84
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,970
You sleep on the bed by yourself

85
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,320
without telling me.

86
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:09,880
Fine.

87
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,320
I'll sleep on the floor.

88
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,730
Lu Jingheng, stop fooling around.

89
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,440
Lu Jingheng,

90
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,480
are you asleep or not?

91
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,840
Is he really asleep

92
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,360
or just pretending?

93
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,200
Fell asleep so fast.

94
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:18,280
What did you do to get so tired?

95
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,520
I drank too much last night

96
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:09,050
and caused you two trouble.

97
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,040
I came here specifically to apologize today.

98
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,770
Mrs. Lu, you don't mind, do you?

99
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,880
It's no big deal.

100
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,680
Jingheng.

101
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:18,000
The black tea Mrs. Wang gave us yesterday,

102
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,160
brew a pot for Miss Wen.

103
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,240
Let's not neglect our guest.

104
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,370
I'll go make the tea.

105
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,400
You two can chat.

106
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,200
What else?

107
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,440
I'll go with you.

108
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:28,180
What's wrong with me chatting with Miss Wen?

109
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,440
Okay, I'll go make some tea.

110
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,400
Zhixia is outspoken.

111
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:35,480
If she offended you in any way,

112
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,540
please don't mind.

113
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,600
Afraid I'll bully your childhood sweetheart?

114
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,330
You're already defending her.

115
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,720
Mrs. Lu is outspoken.

116
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,120
I am just petty.

117
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,060
You guys are too slow. I'll go.

118
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:45,800
I'll go.

119
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,600
You guys chat.

120
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,600
Mrs. Lu.

121
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,580
Jingheng really cares about you.

122
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:59,240
He's afraid we'll argue if left alone,

123
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,180
so he blocked my words beforehand

124
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,420
to keep me from getting angry.

125
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,440
That's what he meant.

126
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,920
And I thought he was protecting you.

127
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,280
Mrs. Lu.

128
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,400
Jingheng and I grew up together.

129
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,860
You seem to mind that a lot.

130
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,400
I wouldn't mind

131
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,840
telling you about our past.

132
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,840
Stop right there.

133
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,460
I don't want to hear it.

134
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,760
But I want to get to know you.

135
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,520
Do you have any favorite sports?

136
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:25,120
Swimming, running, or boxing?

137
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,520
It seems you don't like it.

138
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,680
Then have some fruit and tea

139
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,100
while you wait for him.

140
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,050
I've never been good at sports.

141
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,130
I never liked drinking tea in the past.

142
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:42,640
Mrs. Lu.

143
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,600
It seems you have completely forgotten

144
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,040
our past together.

145
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,880
What do you mean?

146
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,440
Things from the past?

147
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,980
Was she very close to the original owner?

148
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,960
My memory hasn't been good lately.

149
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,720
Miss Wen doesn't like tea.

150
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,680
What would you like to drink then?

151
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,810
I'll have them change it immediately.

152
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,520
No need to bother.

153
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,020
I have things to do. I'll leave first.

154
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,160
Shen Zhixia.

155
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,240
Your pretending not to remember anything

156
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,040
makes you even more disgusting.

157
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:19,200
What exactly is her relationship with the original host?

158
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,640
They seem very close.

159
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,340
Why didn't anyone tell me?

160
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,240
Where is Shuyi?

161
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,240
She left.

162
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,930
You guys didn't fight, did you?

163
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,720
Why would we fight?

164
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,080
Am I close to her?

165
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,760
No.

166
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,560
If it bothers you,

167
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:47,040
I can stop seeing her.

168
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,650
Why would I mind if we're not close?

169
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:51,280
Did I offend her,

170
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,640
or did she offend me?

171
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,440
Tell me more.

172
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:56,560
Rest assured.

173
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,720
Since I've chosen someone,

174
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:01,080
I only have her in my heart.

175
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:04,300
You really just say whatever comes to your mind.

176
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,720
Why are you making no sense?

177
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,760
Forget it.

178
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,720
Let me ask you a question.

179
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:12,280
If two people used to be very close,

180
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,320
but now pretend not to know each other,

181
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:16,880
what kind of relationship is that?

182
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:20,300
Wen Shuyi must have said something to her

183
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,980
that made her misunderstand.

184
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,610
Don't overthink it.

185
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,960
There is no history between us.

186
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:32,040
Wen Shuyi and I are completely innocent.

187
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:36,720
Nothing happened last night.

188
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,880
I was afraid you'd worry,

189
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:40,680
and I couldn't reach the driver.

190
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,040
I walked home by myself.

191
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:47,120
What does this have to do with my question?

192
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,210
What does it have to do with you?

193
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,490
It has nothing to do with me.

194
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,800
I'm asking

195
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:55,160
what my relationship with Wen Shuyi is.

196
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,120
Was I not obvious enough?

197
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,760
I have some things to do.

198
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:05,960
I'll head back first.

199
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,680
Wait.

200
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:09,440
Was I close to Wen Shuyi before?

201
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,040
I haven't heard her mention it.

202
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:12,880
Why did you say you walked back yesterday?

203
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:13,680
How long did it take?

204
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:15,540
How many kilometers did you walk?

205
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,680
Why are these two so strange?

206
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:20,040
When on earth can I

207
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:22,500
find out the truth about the original owner?

208
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:24,680
So annoying.

